  "body": "When i request data early than block #1305087 (0x13e9ff), the request fails w/o an error, and the geth client logs a runTime error. this may be a result of using `--fast`.\n#### System information\n\nGeth version: `Geth/v1.3.6/linux/go1.5.1`\nOS & Version: Linux/Ubuntu\nCommit hash : recent docker image\n#### Expected behaviour\n\nHandle request or respond with error\n#### Actual behaviour\n\nConnection is dropped\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n\nnotice the specified blockTag.\n\nblockTag @ #1305087 - WORKS\n\n```\ncurl -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionCount\",\"params\": [\"0x52bc44d5378309ee2abf1539bf71de1b7d7be3b5\", 1305087], \"id\":1}' -X POST https://rpc.metamask.io \n```\n\nblockTag @ #1305086 - CONNECTION DROPPED\n\n```\ncurl -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionCount\",\"params\": [\"0x52bc44d5378309ee2abf1539bf71de1b7d7be3b5\", 1305086], \"id\":1}' -X POST https://rpc.metamask.io \n```\n#### Trace\n\n```\nI0413 22:58:17.057766       1 server.go:1934] http: panic serving 172.17.0.2:58544: runtime error: invalid memory address or nil pointer dereference\ngoroutine 844747 [running]:\nnet/http.(*conn).serve.func1(0xc82038d810, 0x7f0d15653e68, 0xc822237de8)\n    /usr/lib/go/src/net/http/server.go:1287 +0xb5\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/xeth.(*XEth).TxCountAt(0x0, 0xc82433dcb0, 0x2a, 0x40)\n    /build/ethereum-6ZKMRx/ethereum-1.3.6+10wily/obj-x86_64-linux-gnu/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/xeth/xeth.go:473 +0x18\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/api.(*ethApi).GetTransactionCount(0xc82046b380, 0xc825961f90, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0)\n    /build/ethereum-6ZKMRx/ethereum-1.3.6+10wily/obj-x86_64-linux-gnu/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/api/eth.go:215 +0x269\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/api.(*ethApi).Execute(0xc82046b380, 0xc825961f90, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0)\n    /build/ethereum-6ZKMRx/ethereum-1.3.6+10wily/obj-x86_64-linux-gnu/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/api/eth.go:127 +0xa1\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/api.(*MergedApi).Execute(0xc820196f40, 0xc825961f90, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0)\n    /build/ethereum-6ZKMRx/ethereum-1.3.6+10wily/obj-x86_64-linux-gnu/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/api/mergedapi.go:67 +0x35f\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/comms.(*handler).ServeHTTP(0xc8203335c0, 0x7f0d14622618, 0xc824b98bb0, 0xc8225ab500)\n    /build/ethereum-6ZKMRx/ethereum-1.3.6+10wily/obj-x86_64-linux-gnu/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/comms/http.go:126 +0x5c6\ngithub.com/rs/cors.(*Cors).Handler.func1(0x7f0d14622618, 0xc824b98bb0, 0xc8225ab500)\n    /build/ethereum-6ZKMRx/ethereum-1.3.6+10wily/obj-x86_64-linux-gnu/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/Godeps/_workspace/src/github.com/rs/cors/cors.go:122 +0x17e\nnet/http.HandlerFunc.ServeHTTP(0xc8203335e0, 0x7f0d14622618, 0xc824b98bb0, 0xc8225ab500)\n    /usr/lib/go/src/net/http/server.go:1422 +0x3a\nnet/http.serverHandler.ServeHTTP(0xc821a4ef60, 0x7f0d14622618, 0xc824b98bb0, 0xc8225ab500)\n    /usr/lib/go/src/net/http/server.go:1862 +0x19e\nnet/http.(*conn).serve(0xc82038d810)\n    /usr/lib/go/src/net/http/server.go:1361 +0xbee\ncreated by net/http.(*Server).Serve\n    /usr/lib/go/src/net/http/server.go:1910 +0x3f6\n```\n",
